<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="public\css\main.css" />
  <title> Lego Collection</title>
</head>
<body>


  <%- include('partials/navbar') %>
  <div class="container mx-auto p-4 lg:px-0"> 
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <div class="hero py-8 bg-base-200 rounded-lg">
      <div class="hero-content text-center">
        <div class="max-w-md">
          <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold">Welcome</h1>
          <p class="py-6">Unleash your inner talent and embark on a wonderful journey through the colorful products of Lego.</p>
          <a href="/lego/sets"><button class="btn btn-primary">Get Started</button></a>
        </div>
      </div>


    </div>
    <!-- Grid Section -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-4 mt-8">
      <div class="card w-full bg-base-100 shadow-xl">
        <figure>
          <img class="w-full h-64 object-cover" src="https://m.media-amazon.com/images/S/aplus-media-library-service-media/0697fad3-d2b6-421a-8f61-fe71c22b4d6c.__CR0,0,970,600_PT0_SX970_V1___.jpg" alt="Shoes" />
        </figure>

        <div class="card-body">
          <h2 class="card-title">Gears</h2>
          <p>This set  released in America by Samsonite in 1965. It was again released in 1969 as an educational set. It was never, which was released in Europe.</p>
          <div class="card-actions justify-end">
            <a href="/lego/sets/001-1"><button class="btn btn-primary">View</button></a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="card w-full bg-base-100 shadow-xl">
        <figure>

          <img class="w-full h-64 object-cover" src="https://m.media-amazon.com/images/S/aplus-media-library-service-media/0697fad3-d2b6-421a-8f61-fe71c22b4d6c.__CR0,0,970,600_PT0_SX970_V1___.jpg" alt="Shoes" />
        </figure>


        <div class="card-body">
          <h2 class="card-title">Mini Figures</h2>
          <p>Presented to LEGO employees as Christmas gift</p>
          <div class="card-actions justify-end">
            <a href="/lego/sets/2011-2"><button class="btn btn-primary">View</button></a>
          </div>


        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="card w-full bg-base-100 shadow-xl">
        <figure>

          <img class="w-full h-64 object-cover" src="https://m.media-amazon.com/images/S/aplus-media-library-service-media/0697fad3-d2b6-421a-8f61-fe71c22b4d6c.__CR0,0,970,600_PT0_SX970_V1___.jpg" alt="Shoes" />
        </figure>
        <div class="card-body">

          <h2 class="card-title">Building Set</h2>
          <p> Building Set</p>

          <div class="card-actions justify-end">
            <a href="/lego/sets/011-1"><button class="btn btn-primary">View</button></a>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
